{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":713,"text":"When we think of games,\nthere's all kinds of things."},{"time":3183,"text":"Maybe you're ticked off, or maybe,\nyou're looking forward to a new game."},{"time":6592,"text":"You've been up too late playing a game."},{"time":8474,"text":"All these things happen to me."},{"time":9961,"text":"But when we think about games,"},{"time":11420,"text":"a lot of times we think\nabout stuff like this:"},{"time":13614,"text":"first-person shooters, or the big,\nwhat we would call AAA games,"},{"time":16669,"text":"or maybe you're a Facebook game player."},{"time":18567,"text":"This is one my partner and I worked on."},{"time":20466,"text":"Maybe you play Facebook games,\nand that's what we're making right now."},{"time":23793,"text":"This is a lighter form of game."},{"time":25319,"text":"Maybe you think about\nthe tragically boring board games"},{"time":27946,"text":"that hold us hostage\nin Thanksgiving situations."},{"time":30212,"text":"This would be one of the tragically boring\nboard games that you can figure out."},{"time":33975,"text":"Or maybe you're in your living room,"},{"time":35764,"text":"playing with the Wii with the kids,"},{"time":37645,"text":"and there's this whole range of games,\nand that's very much what I think about."},{"time":41403,"text":"I make my living from games,\nI've been lucky enough to do this"},{"time":44368,"text":"since I was 15, which also qualifies\nas I've never really had a real job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":47829,"text":"But we think about games as fun,\nand that's completely reasonable,"},{"time":51731,"text":"but let's just think about this."},{"time":53369,"text":"So this one here,\nthis is the 1980 Olympics."},{"time":56099,"text":"Now I don't know where you guys were,"},{"time":57948,"text":"but I was in my living room."},{"time":59347,"text":"It was practically a religious event."},{"time":61173,"text":"And this is when the Americans\nbeat the Russians,"},{"time":63784,"text":"and this was --\nyes, it was technically a game."},{"time":66047,"text":"Hockey is a game."},{"time":67398,"text":"But really, was this a game?"},{"time":69168,"text":"I mean, people cried."},{"time":70931,"text":"I've never seen my mother cry\nlike that at the end of Monopoly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74296,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":75462,"text":"And so this was an amazing experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77838,"text":"Or, if anybody here is from Boston --"},{"time":80372,"text":"So when the Boston Red Sox\nwon the World Series"},{"time":83449,"text":"after I believe, 351 years --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":86380,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":87681,"text":"when they won the World Series,\nit was amazing."},{"time":89964,"text":"I happened to be living\nin Springfield at the time,"},{"time":92386,"text":"and the best part of it was,"},{"time":94405,"text":"you would close the women's door\nin the bathroom,"},{"time":97042,"text":"and I remember seeing \"Go Sox,\"\nand I thought, really?"},{"time":99957,"text":"Or the houses, you'd come out,\nbecause every game,"},{"time":103030,"text":"well, I think almost every game,\nwent into overtime, right?"},{"time":105838,"text":"So we'd be outside, and all the other\nlights are on in the whole block."},{"time":109211,"text":"And kids -- the attendance\nwas down in school,"},{"time":112295,"text":"kids weren't going to school,\nbut it's OK, it's the Red Sox, right?"},{"time":115467,"text":"I mean, there's education,\nand then there's the Red Sox,"},{"time":118138,"text":"and we know where they're stacked."},{"time":119927,"text":"So this was an amazing experience,"},{"time":121772,"text":"and again, yes, it was a game,\nbut they didn't write newspaper articles,"},{"time":125285,"text":"people didn't say, \"You know, really,\nI can die now, because the Red Sox won.\""},{"time":129628,"text":"And many people did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131102,"text":"So games, it means something more to us."},{"time":134071,"text":"It absolutely means something more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135964,"text":"So now, this is an abrupt transition here."},{"time":138237,"text":"There was three years where\nI actually did have a real job, sort of."},{"time":141563,"text":"I was the head of a college\ndepartment teaching games,"},{"time":144143,"text":"so, again, it was sort of a real job,"},{"time":145942,"text":"and now I got to talk about making them\nas opposed to making them."},{"time":149603,"text":"Part of the job of it,\nwhen you're a chair of a department,"},{"time":152899,"text":"is to eat, and I did that very well --"},{"time":154733,"text":"and so I'm out at a dinner\nwith this guy called Zig Jackson."},{"time":157598,"text":"So this is Zig in this photograph,\nthis is also one of Zig's photographs."},{"time":161176,"text":"He's a photographer."},{"time":162361,"text":"And he goes all around the country\ntaking pictures of himself,"},{"time":167427,"text":"and you can see here he's got\nZig's Indian Reservation."},{"time":171126,"text":"And this particular shot --"},{"time":172670,"text":"this is one of the more traditional shots."},{"time":175819,"text":"This is a rain dancer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177506,"text":"And this is one of my favorite shots here."},{"time":179628,"text":"So you can look at this, and maybe\nyou've even seen things like this."},{"time":182907,"text":"This is an expression of culture, right?"},{"time":184855,"text":"And this is actually\nfrom his Degradation series."},{"time":187424,"text":"And what was most fascinating\nto me about this series"},{"time":189927,"text":"is just, look at that little boy there,\ncan you imagine?"},{"time":192583,"text":"We can see that's\na traditional Native American."},{"time":194858,"text":"Now I just want to change that guy's race."},{"time":196920,"text":"Just imagine if that's a black guy."},{"time":198841,"text":"So, \"Honey, come here, let's get you\na picture with the black guy.\" Right?"},{"time":202345,"text":"Like, seriously, nobody would do this."},{"time":204179,"text":"It baffles the mind."},{"time":205588,"text":"And so Zig, being Indian,\nlikewise it baffles his mind."},{"time":208493,"text":"His favorite photograph --"},{"time":209763,"text":"my favorite photograph of his,\nwhich I don't have in here --"},{"time":212665,"text":"is Indian taking picture of white people\ntaking pictures of Indians."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215928,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":217462,"text":"So I happen to be at dinner\nwith this photographer,"},{"time":219881,"text":"and he was talking\nwith another photographer"},{"time":221956,"text":"about a shooting that had occurred,"},{"time":223669,"text":"and it was on an Indian Reservation."},{"time":225413,"text":"He'd taken his camera up there\nto photograph it,"},{"time":227693,"text":"but when he got there,\nhe discovered he couldn't do it."},{"time":230297,"text":"He just couldn't capture the picture."},{"time":232103,"text":"And so they were talking back and forth\nabout this question."},{"time":235022,"text":"Do you take the picture or not?"},{"time":236964,"text":"And that was fascinating\nto me as a game designer,"},{"time":239369,"text":"because it never occurs to me,"},{"time":240824,"text":"should I make the game\nabout this difficult topic or not?"},{"time":243996,"text":"Because we just make things that are fun"},{"time":245934,"text":"or will make you feel fear,\nthat visceral excitement."},{"time":249439,"text":"But every other medium does it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251420,"text":"So this is my kid."},{"time":252613,"text":"This is Maezza, and when she was\nseven years old,"},{"time":255310,"text":"she came home from school one day,"},{"time":256974,"text":"and like I do every single day,\nI asked her, \"What did you do today?\""},{"time":260252,"text":"So she said, \"We talked\nabout the Middle Passage.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":262622,"text":"Now, this was a big moment.\nMaezza's dad is black,"},{"time":265000,"text":"and I knew this day was coming."},{"time":267623,"text":"I wasn't expecting it at seven,\nI don't know why, but I wasn't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270763,"text":"Anyways, so I asked her,\n\"How do you feel about that?\""},{"time":274140,"text":"So she proceeded to tell me,"},{"time":275721,"text":"and so any of you who are parents\nwill recognize the bingo buzzwords here."},{"time":279254,"text":"\"The ships start in England,\nthey come down from England,"},{"time":281951,"text":"they go to Africa,\nthey go across the ocean --"},{"time":284165,"text":"that's the Middle Passage part --"},{"time":285834,"text":"they come to America, where\nthe slaves are sold,\" she's telling me."},{"time":289057,"text":"But Abraham Lincoln was elected president,"},{"time":291089,"text":"and then he passed\nthe Emancipation Proclamation,"},{"time":293404,"text":"and now they're free."}]},{"cues":[{"time":294595,"text":"Pause for about 10 seconds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":295923,"text":"\"Can I play a game, Mommy?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":297261,"text":"And I thought, that's it?\nAnd so, you know,"},{"time":299373,"text":"this is the Middle Passage,\nthis is an incredibly significant event,"},{"time":305185,"text":"and she's treating it like, basically\nsome black people went on a cruise,"},{"time":309124,"text":"this is more or less how it sounds to her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":311156,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":312337,"text":"And so, to me,\nI wanted more value in this,"},{"time":315227,"text":"so when she asked\nif she could play a game, I said, \"Yes.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":318431,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":319640,"text":"And so I happened to have\nall of these little pieces."},{"time":322145,"text":"I'm a game designer, so I have\nthis stuff sitting around my house."},{"time":325268,"text":"I said, \"Yeah, you can play a game,\"\nand I give her a bunch of these,"},{"time":328545,"text":"and I tell her to paint them\nin different families."},{"time":330979,"text":"These are pictures of Maezza\nwhen she was --"},{"time":333090,"text":"God, it still chokes me up seeing these."},{"time":335056,"text":"So she's painting her little families."},{"time":336905,"text":"So then I grab a bunch of them\nand I put them on a boat."},{"time":339565,"text":"This was the boat,\nit was made quickly, obviously."},{"time":342476,"text":"And so the basic gist of it is,\nI grabbed a bunch of families,"},{"time":345441,"text":"and she's like, \"Mommy,\nbut you forgot the pink baby"},{"time":347901,"text":"and you forgot the blue daddy"},{"time":349343,"text":"and you forgot all these other things.\""},{"time":351239,"text":"And she says, \"They want to go.\""},{"time":352801,"text":"And I said, \"Honey,\nno, they don't want to go."},{"time":355041,"text":"This is the Middle Passage, Nobody wants\nto go on the Middle Passage.\""},{"time":358370,"text":"So she gave me a look that only a daughter\nof a game designer would give a mother,"},{"time":362276,"text":"and as we're going across the ocean,\nfollowing these rules,"},{"time":365072,"text":"she realizes that she's rolling\npretty high,"},{"time":367155,"text":"and she says to me,\n\"We're not going to make it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":369468,"text":"And she realizes,\nwe don't have enough food,"},{"time":371609,"text":"and so she asks what to do,"},{"time":372950,"text":"and I say -- remember, she's seven --"},{"time":375704,"text":"\"We can either put\nsome people in the water"},{"time":377764,"text":"or we can hope that they don't get sick"},{"time":379659,"text":"and we make it to the other side.\""},{"time":381305,"text":"Just the look on her face came over --"},{"time":383900,"text":"now mind you this is after a month of --"},{"time":386551,"text":"this is Black History Month, right?"},{"time":388254,"text":"After a month, she says to me,\n\"Did this really happen?\""},{"time":392200,"text":"And I said, \"Yes.\" And so she said --"},{"time":395010,"text":"this is her brother and sister --"},{"time":396681,"text":"\"If I came out of the woods,\nAvalon and Donovan might be gone.\""},{"time":399683,"text":"\"Yes.\""},{"time":400874,"text":"\"But I'd get to see them in America.\""},{"time":402706,"text":"\"No.\""},{"time":403881,"text":"\"But what if I saw them?\nCouldn't we stay together?\""},{"time":406434,"text":"\"So Daddy could be gone.\""},{"time":407709,"text":"\"Yes.\""},{"time":408891,"text":"She was fascinated by this,\nand she started to cry,"},{"time":411352,"text":"I started to cry, her father started\nto cry, and now we're all crying."},{"time":414775,"text":"He didn't expect to come home from work\nto the Middle Passage, but there it goes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418672,"text":"And so, we made this game, and she got it."},{"time":420789,"text":"She got it because she spent time\nwith these people."},{"time":423369,"text":"It wasn't abstract stuff\nin a brochure or in a movie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":426638,"text":"And so it was just an incredibly\npowerful experience."},{"time":429730,"text":"This is the game, which I've ended up\ncalling \"The New World,\""},{"time":432734,"text":"because I like the phrase."},{"time":434040,"text":"I don't think the New World\nfelt too new worldly exciting"},{"time":436848,"text":"to the people who were\nbrought over on slave ships."}]},{"cues":[{"time":439303,"text":"But when this happened,\nI saw the whole planet; I was so excited."},{"time":442413,"text":"I'd been making games for 20-some years,"},{"time":444823,"text":"and then I decided to do it again."},{"time":446846,"text":"My history is Irish."},{"time":448286,"text":"So this is a game called \"Síochán Leat.\"\nIt's \"peace be with you.\""},{"time":451442,"text":"It's the entire history\nof my family in a single game."}]},{"cues":[{"time":453997,"text":"I made another game called \"Train.\""},{"time":456520,"text":"I was making a series of six games\nthat covered difficult topics,"},{"time":459599,"text":"and if you're going to cover a difficult\ntopic, this is one you need to cover,"},{"time":463333,"text":"and I'll let you figure out\nwhat that's about on your own."}]},{"cues":[{"time":466085,"text":"And I also made a game\nabout the Trail of Tears."},{"time":468962,"text":"This is a game\nwith 50,000 individual pieces."},{"time":471440,"text":"I was crazy when I decided to start it,\nbut I'm in the middle of it now."},{"time":474848,"text":"It's the same thing."},{"time":476099,"text":"I'm hoping that I'll teach\nculture through these games."}]},{"cues":[{"time":479050,"text":"And the one I'm working\non right now, which is --"},{"time":481376,"text":"because I'm right in the middle of it,"},{"time":483226,"text":"and these for some reason\nchoke me up like crazy --"},{"time":485716,"text":"is a game called\n\"Mexican Kitchen Workers.\""},{"time":487795,"text":"And originally, it was\na math problem, more or less."},{"time":490264,"text":"Here's the economics\nof illegal immigration."},{"time":492355,"text":"And the more I learned\nabout Mexican culture --"},{"time":494580,"text":"my partner is Mexican —\nthe more I learned that,"},{"time":496874,"text":"you know, for all of us,\nfood is a basic need,"},{"time":499228,"text":"and it is obviously with Mexicans, too,\nbut it's much more than that."},{"time":502558,"text":"It's an expression of love.\nIt's an expression of --"},{"time":505012,"text":"God, I'm totally choking up\nway more than I thought."},{"time":507486,"text":"I'll look away from the picture."},{"time":509382,"text":"It's an expression of beauty,\nit's how they say they love you."},{"time":512702,"text":"It's how they say they care,"},{"time":514078,"text":"and you can't hear somebody\ntalk about their Mexican grandmother"},{"time":517130,"text":"without saying \"food\"\nin the first sentence."},{"time":519987,"text":"And so to me, this beautiful culture,"},{"time":522167,"text":"this beautiful expression is something\nthat I want to capture through games."}]},{"cues":[{"time":526511,"text":"And so games, for a change,\nit changes how we see topics,"},{"time":530036,"text":"it changes our perceptions\nabout those people in topics,"},{"time":533572,"text":"and it changes ourselves."},{"time":535318,"text":"We change as people through games,"},{"time":537531,"text":"because we're involved, and we're playing,"},{"time":539591,"text":"and we're learning as we do so."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541104,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}